      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HOOKED ON KISSES (8) resumed in a Grade 5 at Q Straight and finished fourth over 350m (19.15). Solid record here winning two races. The form from her last run stacks up well. Better than last start and worth following up. HUCKLEBERRY HUGO (2) doesn't win out of turn but recent form sound. Has been in the minors the last two runs, the latest finishing third (25.71) at this track. Has a good record at this journey. Well-placed to take this out. COPY THAT (1) hit the ground running to lead before holding on for a placings when second (25.83) at Grafton in Grade 5. Failed to fire only run here. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Will give a great sight again. CRAVEN (6) missed the placings here last start but is well-placed to turn the form around.",
